msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"No, even if the person inside the suit were\n"
"unconscious, they could still stand up like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"Because that Robo Justice suit had a <CLT 3>certain\n"
"characteristic<CLT>..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"You totally can't bend at the waist! Seems like a\n"
"pretty obvious oversight..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"That's right! They totally made a mistake when they\n"
"made it, so it couldn't bend at the waist!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid "I'm not so sure that was a mistake..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"I think the suit was designed from the beginning to be\n"
"used the way it was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Ngh...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"Celeste and Hifumi took the suit they'd specially\n"
"designed and stuffed Hiro into it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid "That's how they were able to fake that whole thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"The point of it all was to make us believe whoever was\n"
"in the suit was to blame!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "Ngh-gh-gh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid "Well then, I suppose this is checkmate..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid "Checkmate...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0015"
msgid "Heh...hehehe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid "Hah...haha...hahaha..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"Don't make me laugh, you idiot! What do you mean,\n"
"checkmate!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid "C-Celeste...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"Clearly, you want to cram me into your little \"guilty\"\n"
"box. Well there's one little problem!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"Have you already forgotten what Hifumi told us as he\n"
"lay dying!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid "Hey, Hifumi! Who was it? Who attacked you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid "Who tried to kill you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid "Who...killed me...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid "That's right... I remember...their name..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid "Y...Yasu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid "...hi...ro..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"When we asked him who had attacked him, his answer was\n"
"quite clear, was it not?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid "He said, and I quote, \"<CLT 3>Yasuhiro<CLT>.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid "In other words, Yasuhiro Hagakureeeee!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"W-Wait, but my name isn't really Yasuhiro! It's\n"
"actually Taro!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"Your confusing statements don't make any sense. You're\n"
"only making things more complicated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"He did say Yasuhiro, but are we sure he was really\n"
"pointing the finger at Hiro?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid ""
"What the hell are you talking about!? I'll burn you\n"
"alive!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Kyoko...what do you mean by that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid "He said people's last names"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid "He said \"for serious\" a lot"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "Wait, isn't that me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Oh yeah... That's kinda the thing you say, huh?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Looks like I just embarrassed myself\n"
"in front of everyone...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "He gave everyone nicknames"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Actually, no...they weren't that close...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Looks like I just embarrassed myself\n"
"in front of everyone...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid "Think about it. How did he used to refer to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>That's right... He always called me \"Mr. Naegi.\" I\n"
"remember that really well.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Looks like I just embarrassed myself\n"
"in front of everyone...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid "Think back to how Hifumi used to talk to us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "How did he refer to each of us?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0048"
msgid ""
"...That's right! Our <CLT 3>last names<CLT>! He called us all by\n"
"our last names!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid ""
"Exactly. I know I heard him say \"<CLT 3>Mr. Naegi<CLT>\" more\n"
"than once, for example."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid ""
"So if Hifumi *did* mean to say Hiro's name, he would\n"
"have said his last name—<CLT 3>Hagakure<CLT>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid ""
"I'm sure it was just incidental—by chance he just—his\n"
"first name...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid "Indecent...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "Don't talk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"Random chance... Now isn't that a convenient\n"
"explanation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"No, there's no reason to think he would have said the\n"
"name any different than normal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"But he must have run out of energy before he could say\n"
"any more."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"So Hifumi was trying to tell us the last name of\n"
"whoever killed him...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid "But the name he said doesn't apply to anyone here..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"Well, no, hold on...there's one person it *could*\n"
"apply to..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid ""
"And that's <CLT 3>Celeste<CLT>. She never actually told us\n"
"what her real name is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid "Wh...? What did you just say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid ""
"To think you'd take your false accusations so far... I\n"
"don't know whether to laugh or spit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid ""
"Come on! Enough with your idiotic blather! Yasuhiro is\n"
"a loser's name! Do I look like a loser to you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid "Well!? Dooooo I!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid ""
"What!? I think I've earned the right to be a little on\n"
"edge!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid "Okay, then fill us in... What's your real name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid ""
"Fine! Make sure your ear holes are wiiiiiiide open and\n"
"listen up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid ""
"My real name is Celestia Ludenberg! Could you PLEASE\n"
"stop making me repeat myself over and over again!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Celeste still won't give up. So then...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>I have to do something to make her accept it!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
